tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE transactions (
  transaction_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  timestamp TIMESTAMP,
  amount DECIMAL,
  description TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE liquidity (
  liquidity_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  date DATE,
  cash_balance DECIMAL,
  liquidity_ratio DECIMAL
)

CREATE TABLE transactions (transaction_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
                    amount DECIMAL,
                    transaction_date TIMESTAMP,
                    account_id INT,
                    description TEXT)

CREATE TABLE accounts (account_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
                    account_name TEXT,
                    account_type TEXT,
                    balance DECIMAL)

CREATE TABLE categories (category_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
                    category_name TEXT)

CREATE TABLE transaction_categories (transaction_id INT,
                    category_id INT,
                    FOREIGN KEY (transaction_id) REFERENCES transactions(transaction_id),
                    FOREIGN KEY (category_id) REFERENCES categories(category_id))

CREATE TABLE Transactions (
    transaction_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    transaction_date TIMESTAMP,
    amount DECIMAL,
    transaction_type VARCHAR(50),
    description TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE Accounts (
    account_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    account_name VARCHAR(100),
    account_type VARCHAR(50),
    balance DECIMAL
)

CREATE TABLE Users (
    user_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    username VARCHAR(50),
    email VARCHAR(100),
    role VARCHAR(50)
)

CREATE TABLE Payments (
    payment_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    payment_date TIMESTAMP,
    amount DECIMAL,
    payee VARCHAR(100),
    payer VARCHAR(100)
)

CREATE TABLE Balances (
    balance_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    account_id UUID,
    balance_date TIMESTAMP,
    balance DECIMAL
)
